{html}<div><p>The below code snippet dies a horrible death:</p>
<pre>
<code class="javascript">    var rows = [];
    var picker = Ti.UI.createPicker();
    picker.add(rows);</code>
</pre>
<p>I think it should be possible to set an empty array as the rows.
I realize it does not make too much sense but one could e.g add
rows later to the picker. It's unexpected that the application
crashes, in my opinion.</p></div>{html}
